%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': {'fontFamily': 'monospace'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant BR as Browser (user)
    participant SV as server.js
    participant PA as lib/parser.js
    participant BF as Backup Files (disk)
    participant CA as cache/parsed.json

    rect rgb(30, 60, 40)
        Note over BR,CA: Phase 1 — Startup (npm run dev)
        SV->>CA: read snapshot immediately
        CA-->>SV: parsedConfigs[] (fast boot)
        SV->>PA: loadAllConfigs() async
        PA->>BF: read txt per device (discovery → newest HHMM)
        BF-->>PA: raw config text
        PA-->>SV: secRules, natRules, addresses,<br/>vipMap, vipgrpMap, schedules
        SV->>CA: write updated snapshot
    end

    rect rgb(30, 40, 70)
        Note over BR,CA: Phase 2 — Search Request (~realtime)
        BR->>SV: GET /api/data
        SV-->>BR: JSON (parsedConfigs[])
        BR->>BR: buildSearchIndex()
        BR->>BR: getFilteredData() on every keystroke
        BR->>BR: renderSecRules / renderNatRules / renderFQDN
    end

    Note over BR,SV: Manual reload
    BR->>SV: POST /api/reload
    SV->>PA: loadAllConfigs()
    PA->>BF: read txt per device
    BF-->>PA: raw config text
    PA-->>SV: updated parsed data
    SV->>CA: write updated snapshot

    Note over SV: cron auto-triggers loadAllConfigs()<br/>at 05:00 and 17:00
